 I like Buku have played alot of classes<br>
 1 60 cleric<br>
 2 60 Shamans (diffrent servers)<br>
 1 60 SK<br>
 1 60 Beastlord<br>
 <br>
  and 3 others all over 55. Druid, Monk, Warrior.<br>
<br>
 I Play them according to my mood, energy, time avail.<br>
<br>
  Yet...for some reason.. I seem to play my Beastlord allmost exclusivly now..It's just a flat out blast to play.<br>
<br>
 Sure we have some problems at the higher levels, Some of these forums are designed to Air them out. It's Needed IMO.<br>
 We are somewhat unfinished.<br>
<br>
  If those that came here to Bitch and moan would bring a solution along with them It would be more constructive, But hey, Some are still working on that toolbox, and I cut em some slack.<br>
<br>
  Playing on Test server, I get a chance to help the class. Thru feedback, Direct contact with testers and Dev team (rarely), I get to feel like I am helping the class in general.<br>
<br>
 I consider it my job to &quot;bitch about the class&quot;. Trust me, It doesn't Endear yourself to the powers that be when you just whine. Have Information available, Focus your feedback in mannor that shows you know what your talking about, Have numbers to back up your statments. <br>
<br>
 In the end, A person simply will not play a class they don't enjoy, the sheer number of Savage Lords and 55+ players that come here should be an indicator of how much the class Is loved. It's also why we fight so hard for the improvements we want/need.<br>
<br>
