Suddenly another potato aggroes and joins the fight - followed by a third!! With the ranger yelling for me to run to the zone gem, I start to move up and melee the third as my pet takes on two... <br>
Granted I had to CH my pet once as we were fighting - it was still a cake battle and I had 75% mana and HP to spare (pet was down to about 65%).<br>
I looted the three corpses and sat by the ranger and said &quot;that was interesting...&quot; <br>
<br>
And he replied (and I quote):<br>
<br>
&quot;I'm logging to create a Beastlord, would you mind if I throw you some tells asking for advice and junk?&quot;<br>
